# Force LF line endings for every text file, even when edited on Windows.
# These dotfiles target Linux; CRLF breaks shells (zsh: "command not found: ^M")
# and "#!" interpreters ("bad interpreter: ...^M"). Git auto-detects binary
# files and leaves them untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly mark known binary assets so they are never touched.
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.png binary
